    "v2.0.0 re-anchored on Amano-style references (docs/art-reference/ + ships_amano/): flowing ink line-art with a vertical colour gradient on the strokes, on a bone-white ground.",
    "THE ORGANISING IDEA: gradient hue encodes depth. Crimson / fire / blood sit at the Surface (despair); the ramp cools through gold and violet into deep navy and ink at the Hadal floor. Chia-green and gold are the recurring accent hues (the Chia-coded pieces, treasure light).",
    "One 32-colour master palette. Pixel profile: sprites snap to it. Illustration profile (ADR-0008): palette is a soft guide; ships_amano ramps live in engine/shipgen/amano_ink.py; composites use bone_white ground.",
    "OQ-11 RESOLVED (ADR-0008): full Amano illustration is the mint medium. Style acceptance: scripts/style_score.py ≥ 92% vs ships_amano + art-reference.",
    "Working palette: swap any hex freely; render_engine and validators read only this file."
  ],
